26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_fb_ram.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:33 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "ram.h"
30
31int
32nvkm_ram_init(struct nvkm_ram *ram)
33{
34 if (ram->func->init)
35 return ram->func->init(ram);
36 return 0;
37}
38
39void
40nvkm_ram_del(struct nvkm_ram **pram)
41{
42 struct nvkm_ram *ram = *pram;
43 if (ram && !WARN_ON(!ram->func)) {
44 if (ram->func->dtor)
45 *pram = ram->func->dtor(ram);
46 nvkm_mm_fini(&ram->tags);
47 nvkm_mm_fini(&ram->vram);
48 kfree(*pram);
49 *pram = NULL;
50 }
51}
52
53int
54nvkm_ram_ctor(const struct nvkm_ram_func *func, struct nvkm_fb *fb,
55 enum nvkm_ram_type type, u64 size, u32 tags,
56 struct nvkm_ram *ram)
57{
58 static const char *name[] = {
59 [NVKM_RAM_TYPE_UNKNOWN] = "of unknown memory type",
60 [NVKM_RAM_TYPE_STOLEN ] = "stolen system memory",
61 [NVKM_RAM_TYPE_SGRAM ] = "SGRAM",
62 [NVKM_RAM_TYPE_SDRAM ] = "SDRAM",
63 [NVKM_RAM_TYPE_DDR1 ] = "DDR1",
64 [NVKM_RAM_TYPE_DDR2 ] = "DDR2",
65 [NVKM_RAM_TYPE_DDR3 ] = "DDR3",
66 [NVKM_RAM_TYPE_GDDR2 ] = "GDDR2",
67 [NVKM_RAM_TYPE_GDDR3 ] = "GDDR3",
68 [NVKM_RAM_TYPE_GDDR4 ] = "GDDR4",
69 [NVKM_RAM_TYPE_GDDR5 ] = "GDDR5",
70 };
71 struct nvkm_subdev *subdev = &fb->subdev;
72 int ret;
73
74 nvkm_info(subdev, "%d MiB %s\n", (int)(size >> 20), name[type]);
75 ram->func = func;
76 ram->fb = fb;
77 ram->type = type;
78 ram->size = size;
79
80 if (!nvkm_mm_initialised(&ram->vram)) {
81 ret = nvkm_mm_init(&ram->vram, 0, size >> NVKM_RAM_MM_SHIFT, 1);
82 if (ret)
83 return ret;
84 }
85
86 if (!nvkm_mm_initialised(&ram->tags)) {
87 ret = nvkm_mm_init(&ram->tags, 0, tags ? ++tags : 0, 1);
88 if (ret)
89 return ret;
90
91 nvkm_debug(subdev, "%d compression tags\n", tags);
92 }
93
94 return 0;
95}
96
97int
98nvkm_ram_new_(const struct nvkm_ram_func *func, struct nvkm_fb *fb,
99 enum nvkm_ram_type type, u64 size, u32 tags,
100 struct nvkm_ram **pram)
101{
102 if (!(*pram = kzalloc(sizeof(**pram), GFP_KERNEL)))
103 return -ENOMEM;
104 return nvkm_ram_ctor(func, fb, type, size, tags, *pram);
105}
